@startuml
title lintree-py Architecture

skinparam componentStyle rectangle

actor User

component "CLI Parser" as CLI
component "LintreeApp" as App
component "TerminalController" as Terminal
component "ScanJob" as Job
component "ConcurrentScanner" as Scanner
component "FileNode Tree" as Tree
component "Treemap Layout" as Layout
component "Canvas Renderer" as Canvas

User --> CLI : start command
CLI --> App : root path, flags
App --> Job : start scan
Job --> Scanner : run worker pool
Scanner --> Tree : populate nodes
App --> Tree : focus and navigation
App --> Layout : visible children
Layout --> App : cells
App --> Canvas : draw frame
Canvas --> Terminal : ANSI output
Terminal --> App : keys and mouse events

note right of Scanner
Skips symlinks and selected
virtual filesystems.
end note

note bottom of Layout
Supports wide horizontal
and square treemap modes.
end note

@enduml
